 Changing colors either disappears or slows down. 

00:02:05.660 --> 00:02:08.140
 Our eyes and brain have evolved to see 

00:02:08.140 --> 00:02:11.860
 but our vision still makes assumptions based on what we have learned, remembered or what we expect. 

00:02:11.860 --> 00:02:14.760
 And all these illusions / tricks take advantage of this. 

00:02:15.020 --> 00:02:17.920
 In fact, it's an advantage to understand information quickly 

